    Paralysis and Grappler converged on Kitkat. The began hitting off the 
Maximals while Guantix and Aerostreak covered the others. Paralysis looked 
around for Quickstrike and Darkmouse...

    Megatron had had enoughof carrying the wasp and threw him into the mud. 
He left his troops to die to save himself, a noble act according to him. A 
wise tyrant always ensures his complete survival in any situation. It was 
only a matter of time before something like this happened.
    "Argh! Get up Waspinator!" He yelled transforming into his beast mode. 
His red eyes scanned the area. It was clear. Besides, who else would be out 
in the middle of the swamps?
    Waspinator reattached his head and stood up a little wobbly, but cought 
himself. He too transformed and wondered what happened while he was in stasis.
    "Megatron, where is Wolfbot and Terrorsaur?" He said looking around, and 
then buzzed up and down.
    Megatron frowned. "We left them. But thats not important now. For right 
now we need to find a shelter....and I have just the place in mind..." He 
said looking up to see the artic mountians to the north.
